data.job_description:
Join our Team!

We are Discovered, an online marketplace for handmade products ethically crafted by artisans in emerging countries. Our mission is to connect artisan entrepreneurs in India, Kenya, Thailand, Indonesia, South America, Mexico, Malaysia and Israel to conscious consumers worldwide. By stocking directly from the makers, every purchase creates a positive impact.

At Discovered, we are a small team with a selection of 75 artisans from all over the world. We have met our makers through our travels and realized they struggle to make ends meet. Solely depending on the local market, it is difficult to sell at reasonable prices, particularly since low quality and industrially produced products have started to appear consistently.

You will…

Plan and create our weekly social media posts and stories on Facebook and Instagram;

Assist in planning creating our weekly newsletters;

Assist in the selection of visuals for different types of content;

Brainstorm about future marketing and social media campaigns

You are…

Passionate about jewelry and sustainable fashion;

A student, or just finished being a student, in a relevant field such as Communication, Marketing, Design, Innovation;

A pro with social media channels;

A fluent English writer, able to write exciting and attractive social media posts and headlines;

Buzzing with creative ideas;

Having a hands-on mentality; you can work independently;

Experienced with design programs like Adobe InDesign, Illustrator and Photoshop, Canvas

We offer…

Hands-on experience in social media and email marketing;

Room for you to discover what you like to do, think creatively and be proactive;

An entrepreneurial start-up environment that gives you space to think independently;

Working with a group of talented, passionate and fun colleagues for a more sustainable fashion sector;

A flexible experience; you can work remotely from any location;

If you are a student from another European country than the Netherlands, this internship is applicable to receive the ERASMUS+ funding;

Relative to your experience, we offer an internship fee of 300 EUR per month for full-time engagement

Practical details

Starting date: As soon as possible

Duration: 4- 6 months internship

Location: Remote

Interested?

Send us your CV and motivation letter in English and, if possible, your portfolio or examples of your work to mark@discovered.us.

We hope to hear from you soon!

Discovered focuses on Marketplaces, Social Commerce, Social Buying, Impact Investing, and Handmade. Their company has offices in Rotterdam and Delaware. They have a small team that's between 1-10 employees.

You can view their website at http://www.discovered.us or find them on Twitter.
